name: Listened to Baby Baku Under The Lights (Toto Was Right)

content.html:
Jessica and Spencer discuss everything on and off the track surrounding the inaugural Las Vegas Grand Prix. A weekend bookended by an exploding water valve causing chaos, ends on a competitive and entertaining race won by Max Verstappen. Spencer was on the ground and gives a first hand insight on what the entire experience was like for himself, the fan perspective and organizers. Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices

By DNF
